Popular triggers
--------
* Git Webhook
* Poll SCM
* Scheduled jobs
* Remote triggers
* Build after other projects are Build

----------------------------------------
Steps
----------------------------------------
* Create git repo
* SSH auth
* Create a Jenkinsfile in git repo & commit
* Create Jenkins job to access Jenkisnfiel from git repo
* Test triggers
________________________________________________________
Create SSH key:
- In git Bash > ssh-keygen.exe \
- ls ~/.ssh/
- cat ~/.ssh/id_rsa.pub
--------------------------------------------------------
Create Repo and clone it to PC in gitbash
